metadata.name: Mannys Crowd #1
metadata.description:
"Mannys Crowd #1" is a crowd of Manny #1's from the [mannys.game](https://mannys.game) collection.

This Mannys Crowd has not yet been merged with any other.

"Mannys Crowd" is a generative art collection inspired by [Crowd by CreatureWorld](https://opensea.io/collection/creaturecrowd) and [mannys.game by mannynotfound](https://mannys.game). The collection may be integrated with ["32 Swords, 32 Mannys"](https://twitter.com/32swords), a deadly on-chain reality show starring 32 Mannys.

"Mannys Crowd" is free to mint for each Manny by its on-chain owner.
